SideMenu

Open during game

shows character and data {
	img of character
	stats {
		attack
		defence
		attack speed
		hunger
		thirst
		
	}

	current items {
		inventory gridlike pattern
		click item to use item

		Items will have a spot predetermined no rearranging for now to keep project simple
	}
}

Tab for
buy menu {
	shows current things unlocked that you can buy
	items
	abilities
	skill upgrades
}

achievements {
	will fill in data
}